Hyrdas lands outside his base. He turns back to the troops not far behind 
him. "No doubt Cyngar will seak shelter with Empath.  I would guess 
Galvatron's base would be the logical place for them to go but I know that 
bases defenses and we arent ready to launch an assault on them with the 
tripred around. Let us go in and plan our next move. I will also have to pick 
a new second in command now that our troops are combined. Whoever desires the 
position and feels can handel it make me know it. Just leave ur name infront 
of my quarters door." He walked into the base and transformed into beast mode 
and  locked his quarters. "Megatron we need to talk about the future. Cyngar 
knows to many secrets of mine we need to eliminate him. If we do the tripred 
may attack us or join forces with Cyngar..also who do you think would be a 
fittign second in command?"

 Proto collapsed ina  chair on the bridge from pure lack of energy. 
Destructor and Quilldart stared eachother down. "We are on the same tream now 
galvatronian dont get any funny ideas" Quilldart stared a hole into his face. 
"I follow Galva's spark till the end...no one elses" He turned and walked 
down the hall.
